Class QPrinter.Unit

public static final class QPrinter.Unit
extends java.lang.Enum
implements QtEnumerator

This enum type is used to specify the measurement unit for page and paper sizes. Note the difference between Point and DevicePixel . The Point unit is defined to be 1/72th of an inch, while the DevicePixel unit is resolution dependant and is based on the actual pixels, or dots, on the printer.
